{"tid":1304881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量] 油塘連儂牆一役","createTime":"2019-07-10T17:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:56:24.000Z","uid":274617,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"adb5d53391b55c5185b82c310430eee3605c74be","tid":1304881,"uid":274617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"經過今晚一役，值得贊既係，大家見到手足被人蝦<br />\n無論你係啱啱放工定食緊飯，住得遠定近，今日DSE放完榜定係已經成家立室甚至有仔有女<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">都願意立刻飛出黎支援撐場</span></strong></span><br />\n果種團結，唔係以前果種網上見到不公義事情但個身體仲留係原地食花生果隻<br />\n檢討係可以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但唔好再話連儂牆無用</span></strong></span><br />\n各區都有好多手足一直冒住風險去做<br />\n你覺得其他方法有用，唔該你自己走出黎去做<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n不分化，不割席，不篤灰<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"cc9958d174083d346174ee7e072378e691b1f363","tid":1304881,"uid":173849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2db6d16ccba9533669fccacbe38dc29918c32651","tid":1304881,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7cc77981f716170360a6d69fe6384b2539d295","tid":1304881,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"連儂牆唔係冇用 但係唔洗放咁多心機去守"},{"pid":"916016cdc54a5761324d1970d726d07ada9cf0a1","tid":1304881,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"今晚開始有少量藍絲街坊斷正左睇到係D休班警恰後生仔，班休班警仲同現場狗係度吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal